00:05:14,165 --> 00:05:22,570
and turning them into mock-ups. We had many, many versions of the house, the lighting condition,

92
00:05:22,570 --> 00:05:28,013
and they were all like, you know, for mood and tone. We, you know, we felt good about these things.

