00:06:21,445 --> 00:06:24,146
No art direction, we had a lot of inspirations.

109
00:06:24,146 --> 00:06:24,946
We were hitting mood.

110
00:06:26,803 --> 00:06:31,665
But a big part of it was that, you know, as part of the gameplay, we had this experiment,

111
00:06:31,665 --> 00:06:34,186
we had a whole house in addition to stories.

112
00:06:34,186 --> 00:06:38,268
There were so many things to build, it was difficult for one person to do it.

113
00:06:38,268 --> 00:06:44,350
And there are parts of it, you know, the essence is there, you know, but there are parts that

114
00:06:44,350 --> 00:06:44,850
were empty.

