00:06:45,777 --> 00:06:50,361
We move forward like you saw in this room was empty.

116
00:06:50,361 --> 00:06:52,703
We had areas that we started.

117
00:06:52,703 --> 00:06:55,506
You're interacting with objects as one of our main mechanics.

118
00:06:55,506 --> 00:06:59,630
And you're jumping from inside a house in one person's body

119
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:02,212
to inside a story in another person's body.

120
00:07:02,212 --> 00:07:05,995
And so this is sort of where I came in

121
00:07:05,995 --> 00:07:08,237
with a team of character artists.

