00:07:08,237 --> 00:07:09,939
And we sort of asked ourselves a question.

123
00:07:09,939 --> 00:07:10,119
Is this?

124
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:17,602
I have some duplicates.

125
00:07:17,602 --> 00:07:18,302
Is this a game?

126
00:07:18,302 --> 00:07:20,723
Are we going to be the indie studio that

127
00:07:20,723 --> 00:07:23,324
makes another game with a person without a body?

128
00:07:23,324 --> 00:07:23,844
You look down.

129
00:07:23,844 --> 00:07:26,385
I mean, there's a lot of challenges.

