And yet, for me, I felt very strongly

134
00:07:33,987 --> 00:07:37,369
that having this moment and the repeated essence of seeing

135
00:07:37,369 --> 00:07:40,130
hands and seeing not your hands was very important.

136
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:43,860
So we started with an outsource,

