00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:46,780
and these were the first two hands in the game.

138
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:49,501
We had Edith and Molly, and it was also,

139
00:07:49,501 --> 00:07:52,522
as I was assuring everyone, don't worry,

140
00:07:52,522 --> 00:07:58,003
every kid can use the same small kid hands.

141
00:07:58,003 --> 00:07:59,863
But it translated what was previously

142
00:07:59,863 --> 00:08:03,824
empty, oh, I can't see what it's playing,

143
00:08:03,824 --> 00:08:05,085
into moments like this.

