00:08:10,152 --> 00:08:15,356
And so, you know, despite the concern that this was not going to be enough time,

145
00:08:15,356 --> 00:08:21,181
or this was not going to be enough bang for the buck, so to speak,

146
00:08:21,181 --> 00:08:22,903
we sort of soldiered on.

147
00:08:22,903 --> 00:08:24,804
You know, we went from moments that had read like this

